{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The children who had families went to the families, and we stayed in a hostel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the poor man didn't know what to do with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Stoke Newington.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The trouble was, you see, we all expected, you know, that we will have a palace-- car waiting for us, a Prince Charming.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody wanted to study medicine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we had high expectations that the-- the Jewish community will-- people didn't know very much about us, didn't know how to treat us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nowadays, if you have some catastrophe, you've got counseling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, people didn't know how to-- we looked normal, but we were not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, we were all damaged in one way or another.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we needed special treatment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we didn't-- we didn't-- we-- people didn't know enough about it to know how to handle us, how to treat us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the poor rabbi-- he had such a difficult time, because everybody pulled him in each way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I reminded myself that before the war, a cousin of my mother's came from London.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I didn't know her name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I knew she wouldn't know my name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I was very keen to lighten of-- to take off the load of his shoulders, because he had got so many problems.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought, if I can just remove myself-- he's done his job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He brought me over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I can do something myself, it would be a help to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he gave an advert to the that the granddaughter of-- is looking for the daughter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I only knew that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she responded to that advert and came to collect me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
